2003/05/28 ({jong,jurgenv}@cwi.nl)
 * Added TERM_SIZE_WARNING_THRESHOLD: when terms bigger than this threshold
   are sent to the ToolBus, a warning is printed. If threshold is set to 0,
   the warning code is disabled.

